1. Svi smo uz* njega u teškim trenucima. (We were all with him in difficult times.)
2. On je uzeo* novi posao u inostranstvu. (He took a new job abroad.)
3. Ona je uzela* novi auto. (She took a new car.)
4. Rekao je da će mi pomoći uz* najbolju namjeru. (He said he would help me with the best intention.)
5. Pridružio se nama uz* veliko zadovoljstvo. (He joined us with great pleasure.)